Rating: 4
This is a huge favorite in our house. I've made it as written - very good, not too sweet for me but still sweet. More frequently I change it up to make it healthier with a mixture of white flour, whole wheat flour and ground flaxseed (you really can't tell it's in there), reducing the sugar to 2 cups, and using 2/3 cup oil and 1/2 cup applesauce. And upping the cinnamon and the nutmeg each to 1.5tsp. Excellent either way and easily modified!

