Rating: 4
I was looking for a quick and easy way to use up some extra canned pumpkin, at the restaurant where I work ,when I tried this recipe. I also doubled the spices and the results were great! However, I wouldn't recommend decreasing the amount of sugar at all. Sugar is Hydroscopic; meaning it absorbs and retains moisture. It makes baked goods moist and gives them a tender crumb. Which is exactly what these loaves have. Next time I will try putting a little streusel topping for extra pizazz.

