A great recipe; I took the advice of several reviewers and modified the recipe slightly which results in a healthier and denser version of the original. After making the 'test' batch the next day I made several loaves for freezing and giving away. Bread tastes much better the next day or at minimum sitting for several hours. Modifications were (2)cups of sugar (1 white and 1 brown); (1/2)cup oil and (1/2) cup unsweetened applesauce; (3)cups of flour but (2 white and 1 whole wheat) and doubled the spices except for the cloves.

